                        <interp inst="t18441021-name-532" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE WILKINS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 133.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
